e rise of math playground car games reflects a broader shift toward experiential and game-based learning. As technology evolves and educators gain more insights into effective digital pedagogy, such games are poised to become an indispensable component of the educational landscape. Balancing engagement with educational rigor remains the key to harnessing their full potential.",
